{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">掌握粗盐提纯的基本方法。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">BaCl<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;Na<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">SO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">4</span></sub>&nbsp;= Ba<span style=\"color:#000000\">SO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">4</span></sub>&darr; + 2NaCl</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">MgCl<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;2NaOH&nbsp;= Mg<span style=\"color:#000000\">(</span>OH<span style=\"color:#000000\">)</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&darr;&nbsp;+ 2NaCl &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">BaCl<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;Na<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">CO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub>&nbsp;= Ba<span style=\"color:#000000\">CO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub>&darr; + 2NaCl</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">C</span>aCl<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub>&nbsp;+&nbsp;Na<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">CO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub>&nbsp;= <span style=\"color:#000000\">C</span>a<span style=\"color:#000000\">CO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub>&darr; + 2NaCl</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Na<sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">2</span></sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">CO</span><sub><span style=\"color:#000000\">3</span></sub><sub>&nbsp;</sub>+&nbsp;2HCl&nbsp;= 2NaCl&nbsp;+&nbsp;H<sub>2</sub>O<sub>&nbsp;</sub>+ CO<sub>2</sub>&uarr;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">NaOH&nbsp;+&nbsp;HCl&nbsp;= NaCl&nbsp;+&nbsp;H<sub>2</sub>O<sub>&nbsp;</sub></span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：铁架台、铁圈、漏斗、烧杯、滤纸、胶头滴管、蒸发皿、玻璃棒、酒精灯、药匙、火柴。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：粗盐、水、氯化钡溶液、稀盐酸、氢氧化钠溶液、碳酸钠溶液。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">取一勺粗盐加到烧杯中，然后加入约20ml蒸馏水，用玻璃棒搅拌加速溶解。过滤，在滤液中依次加入过量氯化钡溶液、过量氢氧化钠溶液和过量碳酸钠溶液。过滤，在滤液中加入过量稀盐酸，然后将溶液倒入蒸发皿中进行蒸发结晶，在溶液量很少时停止加热，利用余热将溶液蒸干。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">加入氯化钡溶液、氢氧化钠溶液和碳酸钠溶液时均有沉淀产生，蒸发过程中有白色固体析出。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}